| evalOP_AppV[intro]:  "\<lbrakk> P \<Down> DBAbsV M; Q \<Down> q; M<q/0> \<Down> V \<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> DBApp P Q \<Down> V" (* Strict application *)
